3. Mandatory Copyleft (Source Disclosure)

If you distribute, publish, deploy, or make the Software available
to users (including Network Use), you MUST:

- provide the complete corresponding source code
- include build scripts and dependencies
- make the source publicly accessible at no charge
- license the entire Derivative Work under this same license

This applies to:

- mobile apps (Android/iOS)
- bots
- SaaS platforms
- servers
- hosted services
- APIs
- any compiled binaries

Closed-source or private forks are NOT permitted.

----------------------------------------------------------------

4. No Proprietary Relicensing

You may NOT:

- relicense under proprietary terms
