- add additional legal or technical restrictions

All Derivative Works must remain open.

----------------------------------------------------------------

5. Attribution Requirement (Mandatory)

Any application, software, service, bot, server, or product
that uses or derives from this Software MUST provide visible attribution.

The following text must be displayed in at least one
publicly accessible location:

"Powered by SPEAR"
or
"Built with SPEAR Technology"

The attribution must:

- be reasonably visible
- not be hidden or obscured
- not be modified or reworded
- include a link to: https://spear.pics

Acceptable locations include:

- About page
- Settings page
- README
- Documentation
- Service description
- Help/about commands (for bots/CLI)

Removal of attribution is a license violation.

